      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you ready for an absolute show-stopper? I'm parting with this total gem, and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! It's been babied since day one, spotless inside and out, and runs like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
